 â In the second load, Gonzalez must find his hammock while avoiding the dangers of a stereotypical Mexican landscape (Indian tribes, wild animals, etc). Weapons and ammunition are scattered in one large level divided in sections. He can collect or drop these by crouching with the &lt;b&gt;A&lt;/b&gt; key and can use them with the &lt;b&gt;SPACE&lt;/b&gt; bar.</description>
